Query
SELECT Customers.customer_id, Customers.first_name, Orders.item
FROM Customers
JOIN Orders
ON Customers.customer_id = Orders.customer;


âœ… Explanation:
This joins the Customers and Orders tables using the customer_id column.

ðŸ§¾ Result:

customer_id	first_name	item
