3	Bob	Tablet
Example 2 â€” Join With WHERE Clause
SELECT Customers.customer_id, Customers.first_name, Orders.amount
FROM Customers
JOIN Orders
ON Customers.customer_id = Orders.customer
WHERE Orders.amount >= 800;


âœ… Explanation:
This returns only those customers whose order amount â‰¥ 800.

